Description_lang: Your Felguard deals $s1% additional damage. Soul Strike now deals $s2% of its damage to nearby enemies.

description_blz.en_US: Your Felguard deals 20% additional damage. Soul Strike now deals 25% of its damage to nearby enemies.
description_blz.es_MX: Tu guardia vil inflige un 20% más de daño. Golpe del alma ahora inflige un 25% de su daño a enemigos cercanos.

description_blz.de_DE: Eure Teufelswache verursacht zusätzlich 20% Schaden. 'Seelenstoß' fügt Gegnern in der Nähe 25% seines Schadens zu.
description_blz.en_GB: Your Felguard deals 20% additional damage. Soul Strike now deals 25% of its damage to nearby enemies.

description_blz.ko_KR: 자신의 지옥수호병이 20%의 추가 피해를 입힙니다. 영혼의 일격은 주위 적에게 입힌 피해의 25%에 해당하는 피해를 입힙니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 你的惡魔守衛額外造成20%傷害。靈魂打擊現在會對附近敵人造成25%傷害。
